---
title: Roasted Pear, Beetroot & Goat's Cheese Salad with Smashed Potatoes and Walnuts
description: This Roasted Pear, Beetroot & Goat's Cheese Salad with Smashed Potatoes and Walnuts is a delicious dinner, which makes the most of so many flavourful festive ingredients.
